          "text": "<br data-start=\"40\" data-end=\"43\">\nA narrow passage around the bridge exterior, providing safe access for inspection and maintenance.<br data-start=\"141\" data-end=\"144\">\n駕駛台外圍的狹長走道，用於人員安全進行檢查與維護。"
