          "pitch": 0.5299206200904969,
          "title": "Lifebuoy",
          "text": "A life-saving buoy located on the bridge wing, released by pulling a pin so it drops directly into the sea. Unlike lifebuoys in other locations, it ensures the fastest response due to wide visibility, and its weight is designed for reliable free-fall release.<br data-start=\"281\" data-end=\"284\">\n駕駛台兩翼的救生圈，透過拔除插銷即可落入海。與其它位置的救生圈不同，此處因視野最廣，可最快速反應，且重量設計適合自由落體釋放。"
