          "title": "<strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"26\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(58, 68, 84, 0.8);\">VDR Float-Free Capsule</strong>",
          "text": "<br data-start=\"26\" data-end=\"29\">\nA buoyant capsule that automatically releases during sinking, storing voyage data for accident investigation.<br data-start=\"138\" data-end=\"141\">\n一種具浮力的艙體，船舶沉沒時自動脫落，保存航行資料以供事故調查。"
