          "text": "<br data-start=\"21\" data-end=\"24\">\nAn emergency layout posted behind student cabin doors, showing exits, routes, and assembly points.<br data-start=\"122\" data-end=\"125\">\n張貼於學生房門後的逃生佈置圖，標示出口、疏散路線與集合地點。"
