          "text": "<br data-start=\"33\" data-end=\"36\">\nStored in student cabins for emergencies: lifejackets provide buoyancy, and immersion suits protect against cold water.<br data-start=\"155\" data-end=\"158\">\n存放於學生房內的救生衣與浸水衣，遇險時使用，前者提供浮力，後者防寒防水。"
