          "text": "<br data-start=\"13\" data-end=\"16\">\nStudent cabins have upper and lower bunks; caution is needed to avoid hitting your head.<br data-start=\"104\" data-end=\"107\">\n學生房間配有上下舖，使用時請小心，避免頭部碰撞。"
