          "text": "<br data-start=\"33\" data-end=\"36\">\nAn outlet supplying conditioned air; airflow volume can be adjusted using the knob.<br data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"122\">\n房間內的中央空調出風口，可透過旋鈕調整送風量。"
