          "title": "<span style=\"font-size: 13px; background-color: rgba(58, 68, 84, 0.8);\">28PS diesel engine (380J-3)</span>",
          "text": "Equipped with a 28PS diesel engine (380J-3) and a 50L fuel tank, allowing 6 persons onboard to travel at over 6 knots for at least 4 hours. Features dual battery starting systems, a manual bilge pump, and comes with tools and engine spares.<br data-start=\"290\" data-end=\"293\">\nF.R.P.救難艇，配備28馬力(380J-3)柴油機與50公升油箱，載6人時可超過6節航速航行至少4小時。設有雙電瓶獨立啟動系統、手搖泵，並附工具與備件。"
