          "text": "A davit system designed to lower boats by their own weight. It can be operated by remote control, brake counterweight, or electric winch, with manual backup in case of power loss. Equipped with a limit switch and interlock for safety. SWL: 23kN (≈2345 kg).<div><br data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"304\">\n單臂回轉式艇架，利用艇自身重量下放水面，可透過遙控鋼纜、剎車重錘或電動絞車操作，斷電時可用手動泵回收。設有限位與連鎖保護，確保安全。安全工作負荷23kN（約2345公斤）。</div>"
