          "text": "<br data-start=\"15\" data-end=\"18\">\nA protruding bulb at the ship’s bow, reducing water resistance and improving fuel efficiency.<br data-start=\"111\" data-end=\"114\">\n位於船艏的球狀突出結構，可降低水阻並提升燃油效率。"
