          "text": "<br data-start=\"30\" data-end=\"33\">\nA high-holding-power stockless anchor widely used on modern ships. Weight tolerance is +7% to –3%. The anchor head (with pin and annexes) must be at least 60% of the total weight. Dimensional tolerance is ±4% (max ±20 mm). All anchors are painted after inspection. Standards: CB/T 3972-2005, CB/T 772-1998.<br data-start=\"339\" data-end=\"342\">\nAC-14型大抓力無杆錨（3668公斤），為現代船舶常用。重量允差 +7% 至 –3%，錨頭含銷與附件需佔總重60%以上。尺寸允差 ±4%（最大 ±20mm）。檢驗合格後須塗裝。依據標準：CB/T 3972-2005、CB/T 772-1998。"
