          "text": "<br data-start=\"44\" data-end=\"47\">\nA remote control panel to discharge CO₂ into protected spaces for firefighting.<br data-start=\"126\" data-end=\"129\">\n設於滅火站的遠端控制系統，可釋放二氧化碳至防護區域以滅火。"
