          "text": "<br data-start=\"30\" data-end=\"33\">\nA control and indicator panel displaying the open/closed status of fire doors throughout the ship.<br data-start=\"131\" data-end=\"134\">\n防火門監測面板，用於顯示並監控全船防火門的開關狀態。"
