          "yaw": -2.1804832675452754,
          "pitch": 0.09081765268426878,
          "title": "Main Switchboard",
          "text": "The primary electrical distribution board located in the Engine Control Room, receiving power from generators and distributing it to shipboard systems with protection and monitoring functions.<br data-start=\"224\" data-end=\"227\">\n機控室主配電盤，接收發電機輸出並分配至全船各用電系統，具備保護與監控功能。"
