          "title": "Engine Room Overhead Crane",
          "text": "An overhead crane (capacity 1.25 tons, proof load 1.56 tons) installed in the engine room for lifting and moving heavy components such as cylinder covers, pistons, and pumps. It has a lifting height of 9.5 m with 4-fall wire rope (Ø6.3 mm), powered by AC 3φ 440V 60Hz, and controlled via AC 1φ 110V circuit. Operation is by 8-point pendant push button with emergency stop. Span 4.2 m, runway distance 13.3 m, weight approx. 1600 kg.<div><br data-start=\"465\" data-end=\"468\">\n機艙吊車，額定起重量 1.25 公噸（試驗荷重 1.56 公噸），用於吊運汽缸蓋、活塞、泵浦等重件。吊升高度 9.5 公尺，4股 Ø6.3 mm 鋼索，電源 AC 三相 440V 60Hz，控制電路 AC 單相 110V。以 8 點吊控按鈕操作，具備緊急停止功能。跨度 4.2 公尺，跑道距離 13.3 公尺，重量約 1600 公斤。</div>"
